reviewText: I bought this as a gift for my nieces' birthday, she loves Dora. This was a great value for the price. She was happy with it and that means I am too. Shipped super fast.

My daughter loved all three videos and watches them constantly. Inside the pack was a card with a picture and recipe for a Dora Castle Cake. Of course that is the cake we wanted to make and now her birthday is Saturday and I cant find the card. If anyone can scan it in and send it to me I would greatly appreciate it. vtcol@yahoo.com.
If your child is a Dora fan he or she will love these DVD's !  Especially if it's his or hers birthday!
